notes.text: This advisory aggregates security fixes for the mecab-ipadic SRPM in CIQ LTS for Rocky Linux 8.6. It addresses 129 CVEs: CVE-2022-21594, CVE-2022-21599, CVE-2022-21604, CVE-2022-21608, CVE-2022-21611, and 124 more.
